items.sentence: Tom hasn't yet been told he shouldn't do that.
Do you think it's going to be easy to do that?
I'd never in a million years actually do that.
Do you think you can help me do that tomorrow?
I just thought it wasn't necessary to do that.
I want to know why you think I should do that.
I think you could've done that if you'd tried.
Tom is never going to agree to do that, is he?
I didn't plan to do that yesterday, but I did.
Are you sure that you can do that by yourself?
